Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.79,0:01:56.15,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H42009A&\c&HFFFFFF&}Pri-Priprema. Iako uopšte nisam toliko jaka.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.99,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HBCD3FF&}pure purepare-do itsuka kimi wo tsukamaeru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.99,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HFFFFFF&}Pri-Priprema. Jednog dana ću te uhvatiti.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.39,0:02:20.17,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFF4C5&}yudan shitara sono yubi chiku chiku atakku kakugo shite
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.39,0:02:20.17,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFFFFF&}Kada ne budeš pazio, očekuj moje prste da krenu u napad golicanjem.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.36,0:02:25.93,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H007D9C&\c&HBBE5F2&}chiisai kedo hasamu no mijinko mitai na anata
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.36,0:02:25.93,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H007D9C&\c&HFFFFFF&}Iako sam mala, zgrabiću te kao mušicu.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.61,0:02:32.49,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HD8D5FF&\3c&H1910BD&}hoshii no wa purasuchikku na ha-to   {\3c&H6A9800&\c&HE8FFB3&}(purasu purasu dakedo mainasu)
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.61,0:02:32.49,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1910BD&}Želim plastično srce.\N{\3c&H6A9800&}(Plus! Plus! Ali onda minus!)
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.49,0:02:39.74,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H42009A&\c&HD7B8FF&}demo sore ja tsumaranai soko ni kizuita mono kachi
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.49,0:02:39.74,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H42009A&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ali to je dosadno, kada bih primetila, pobedila bih.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.41,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HBCD3FF&}koi wa amakute nigai mono
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.41,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ljubav je slatka i gorka stvar,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.54,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFF4C5&}tanjunmeikai fukuzatsukaiki na shiromono
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.54,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFFFFF&}prosta je i jednostavna, složena i zagonetna.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.58,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H007D9C&\c&HBBE5F2&}dou demo ii koto bakkari ki ni shitari suru no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.58,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H007D9C&\c&HFFFFFF&}Samo se brinem o svakakvim stvarima.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.42,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HD8D5FF&\3c&H1910BD&}donna kanji? sonna kanji!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.42,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1910BD&\c&HFFFFFF&}Kakav je osećaj? Takav je osećaj!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.59,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H42009A&\c&HD7B8FF&}onkoutokujitsu ekisentorikku na anata
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.59,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H42009A&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ti si ljubazan i iskren, ali ekscentričan.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.62,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HBCD3FF&}tsuyogaru suburi wo zenshin matotte tachiuchi
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.62,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HFFFFFF&}Pravim se da sam snažna i takmičim se sa tobom.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.43,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFF4C5&}sunao na dake da to shigeki ga tsuyokute kurakura
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.43,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFFFFF&}Samo od toga što sam iskrena osećam se ošamućeno.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.67,0:03:06.70,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H007D9C&\c&HBBE5F2&}kizutsuichau no  kizutsukechau no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.67,0:03:06.70,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H007D9C&\c&HFFFFFF&}Povređena sam, povredila sam te.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.93,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HD8D5FF&\3c&H1910BD&}junjou purepara-to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.93,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1910BD&\c&HFFFFFF&}Naivna priprema.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.69,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H42009A&\c&HD7B8FF&}atama no naka wa   {\3c&H6A9800&\c&HE8FFB3&}(itsumo hitori no)
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.69,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H42009A&}U mojoj glavi   {\3c&H6A9800&}(Uvek sama)
